overview: At "Dark Water," Mike Quackenbush steps back into the ring to finish a rivalry that dates back years! Complicating matters is the addition of an "enforcement official," that being Sidney Bakabella. Dasher Hatfield joins forces with The Rumblebees to take on the treacherous trio of Juan Francisco de Coronado with Crummels and Defarge. Plus, the Young Lions Cup is defended for the final time in Season 18!
title: CHIKARA Dark Water
